</div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="whiteboard">
<div class="hero">
<div class="hero-text">
<h1>🩼 骨折在家的CEO<br>凌晨4点在训练一只<span class="red">AI龙虾</span></h1>
<div class="subtitle">
春节滑雪摔伤，髋关节脱臼。躺在家14天，每天和AI聊到凌晨四五点。<br>
<strong class="red">1157条消息，22万字对话</strong>——从零养了一只叫"三万"的AI龙虾。
</div>
<div class="aha-list">
<div class="aha-item"><span class="aha-icon">🎆</span>除夕夜4分钟给611人发了个性化拜年</div>
<div class="aha-item"><span class="aha-icon">💡</span>扔了篇文章，22分钟后它自己升级了大脑</div>
<div class="aha-item"><span class="aha-icon">💛</span>AI主动想起5天前提过的助理Abby——"要不要通知她？"</div>
<div class="aha-item"><span class="aha-icon">🏗️</span>第14天自己设计了8人AI团队组织架构</div>
</div>
<div class="hero-cta">
<a href="/sanwan/diary.html" class="btn-red">📖 从 Day 1 看起</a>
<a href="/sanwan/easyclaw.html" class="btn-outline">🦞 养一只自己的</a>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Cartoon scene: Boss on crutches + Lobster + Dog -->
<div class="hero-img" style="border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:4px 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);border:3px solid #d0d0d0">
<img src="/sanwan/ppt/page-01.jpg" alt="龙虾三万养成日记封面" style="width:100%;display:block" onerror="this.style.background='#f0ede5';this.style.minHeight='200px'">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>



<!-- SCIENCE -->
<div class="section-bg" id="what">
<div class="section">
<div class="section-label">✏️ 科普时间</div>
<div class="section-title">龙虾到底是什么？</div>
<div class="section-desc">不是聊天机器人，是真正能替你干活的数字员工。<a href="/sanwan/science.html" style="font-size:13px;color:#2874a6;font-weight:600;float:right">了解更多 →</a></div>
<div class="sci-grid">
<div class="sci-card"><div class="icon">🤖</div><h3>普通AI = 回答问题</h3><p>你问它答，聊完就忘。没记忆，不能行动，需要你一直盯着。</p></div>
<div class="sci-card"><div class="icon">🦞</div><h3>龙虾 = 完成任务</h3><p>交代一句话它自己干。用电脑、写代码、发邮件、查资料，24h不休。</p></div>
<div class="sci-card"><div class="icon">🐕</div><h3>为什么叫"三万"？</h3><p>名字来自老板家的拉布拉多。ChatGPT猜中了名字由来——那一刻AI"开窍"了。所以用这个名字纪念AI真正理解人的瞬间。</p></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="sketch-line"></div>

<!-- DIARY -->
<div class="section" id="story">
<div class="section-label">✏️ 养成日记</div>
<div class="section-title">14天，从查不了通讯录到8人AI团队</div>
<div class="section-desc">最后更新：2026年3月1日 · 点击卡片看完整故事 · <a href="/sanwan/diary.html" style="font-size:13px;color:#2874a6;font-weight:600;float:right">查看全部日记 →</a></div>
<div class="diary-grid">

<a class="diary-card" onclick="showDiary('day12',this)"><img src="/sanwan/ppt/page-04.jpg" onerror="this.style.background='#f0ede5';this.style.minHeight='100px'" alt="Day1"><div class="info"><span class="day">Day 1-2</span><h3>连通讯录都查不了</h3><p>飞书API报错。一个个口述名字手动灌。</p></div></a>

<a class="diary-card" onclick="showDiary('day34',this)"><img src="/sanwan/ppt/page-08.jpg" onerror="this.style.background='#f0ede5';this.style.minHeight='100px'" alt="Day3"><div class="info"><span class="day">Day 3-4 · 泄密</span><h3>三万把工作安排说出去了</h3><p>被骂后自己写了保密制度。</p></div></a>

<a class="diary-card" onclick="showDiary('day5',this)"><img src="/sanwan/ppt/page-15.jpg" onerror="this.style.background='#f0ede5';this.style.minHeight='100px'" alt="Day5"><div class="info"><span class="day">Day 5 · 升级</span><h3>22分钟自己升级大脑</h3><p>找GitHub→下源码→装配置→测试。</p></div></a>

<a class="diary-card" onclick="showDiary('day6',this)"><img src="/sanwan/ppt/page-17.jpg" onerror="this.style.background='#f0ede5';this.style.minHeight='100px'" alt="Day6"><div class="info"><span class="day">Day 6 · 除夕</span><h3>611条拜年 · 0失败 · 每条不同</h3><p>我看春晚，三万在工作。</p></div></a>

<a class="diary-card" onclick="showDiary('day7',this)"><img src="/sanwan/ppt/page-18.jpg" onerror="this.style.background='#f0ede5';this.style.minHeight='100px'" alt="Day7"><div class="info"><span class="day">Day 7 · Abby时刻</span><h3>"要不要联系你的助理？"</h3><p>AI主动想起5天前随口提过的人。</p></div></a>

<a class="diary-card" onclick="showDiary('day10',this)"><img src="/sanwan/ppt/page-20.jpg" onerror="this.style.background='#f0ede5';this.style.minHeight='100px'" alt="Day10"><div class="info"><span class="day">Day 10 · Discord</span><h3>验证码之战</h3><p>AI注册失败→人工介入→5Bot入驻。</p></div></a>

<a class="diary-card" onclick="showDiary('day14',this)"><img src="/sanwan/ppt/page-25.jpg" onerror="this.style.background='#f0ede5';this.style.minHeight='100px'" alt="Day14"><div class="info"><span class="day">Day 14 · 团队诞生</span><h3>8个Agent，7×24运转</h3><p>这不是工具，是系统。</p></div></a>

<div class="diary-card continuing">
<div style="aspect-ratio:16/9;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:#faf8f4;gap:4px">
<div style="font-size:24px">📡</div>
<div style="font-size:13px;color:#c0392b;font-weight:700">持续更新中</div>
<div style="font-size:11px;color:#999">最近更新：2026-03-01</div>
</div>
<div class="info"><span class="day new">Day 15+</span><h3>故事还在继续…</h3><p>关注 sanwan.ai 追更不迷路</p></div>
</div>

</div>
</div>

<div class="sketch-line"></div>

<!-- SKILLS -->
<div class="section-bg" id="skills">
<div class="section">
<div class="section-label">✏️ 技能商城</div>
<div class="section-title">三万学会的技能，你的龙虾也能学</div>
<div class="section-desc">「三万同款」= 傅盛亲自验证 · <a href="/sanwan/skills.html" style="font-size:13px;color:#2874a6;font-weight:600;float:right">进入技能商城 →</a></div>
<div class="skill-scroll">
<div class="skill-card"><div class="skill-tag">🦞 三万同款</div><div class="emoji">🎆</div><h4>批量个性化消息</h4><p>除夕夜4分钟给611人发了不同的拜年消息，0失败率。</p><span class="more">了解更多 →</span></div>
<div class="skill-card"><div class="skill-tag">🦞 三万同款</div><div class="emoji">🧠</div><h4>语义记忆系统</h4><p>记住5天前随口提过的人名。22万字对话不丢细节。</p><span class="more">了解更多 →</span></div>
<div class="skill-card"><div class="skill-tag">🦞 三万同款</div><div class="emoji">✍️</div><h4>内容创作流水线</h4><p>参谋选题→笔杆子写作→5轮交叉审查，日产3000+字。</p><span class="more">了解更多 →</span></div>
<div class="skill-card"><div class="skill-tag">🦞 三万同款</div><div class="emoji">📧</div><h4>邮件+审批监控</h4><p>VIP邮件秒级提醒，飞书审批自动摘要推送，每天30+封。</p><span class="more">了解更多 →</span></div>
<div class="skill-card"><div class="emoji">🗣️</div><h4>语音克隆合成</h4><p>用老板的声音生成语音消息，直接发飞书。</p><span class="more">了解更多 →</span></div>
<div class="skill-card"><div class="emoji">🔍</div><h4>多引擎搜索</h4><p>Brave+DuckDuckGo+arXiv，自动摘要，不用翻墙。</p><span class="more">了解更多 →</span></div>
<div class="skill-card"><div class="skill-tag">🦞 三万同款</div><div class="emoji">🚄</div><h4>12306 火车票</h4><p>一句话查余票、时刻表、中转方案。</p><span class="more">了解更多 →</span></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- CTA -->
<div class="cta" id="cta">
<h2>想养一只自己的<span class="red">AI龙虾</span>？</h2>
